== Ezekiel achem Pustok ==
'''Book of Ezekiel'''

[[File:Flemish - Ezekiel's Vision of the Sign "Tau" (Ezekiel IX -2-7) - Walters 44616.jpg|thumb|A mid-12th century Flemish piece of copperwork depicting Ezekiel's Vision of the Sign "Tau" from Ezekiel IX:2-7. The item is currently held by the Walters Museum.]]
